The queue class adds a type field in the payload which is not required. E.g.

2016-01-06 09:29:38,832 [INFO] method=POST uri=/v1/metrics
2016-01-06 09:29:38,832 [INFO] body(->): {"gauges": [{"measure_time": 1452094140, "source": "foo", **"type": "gauge"**, "name": "flask.app.response.latency.median", "value": 1.5305279999999999}, {"measure_time": 1452094140, "source": "foo", "type": "gauge", "name": "flask.app.response.latency.upper_95", "value": 1.08695}]}
